    <text>
        <body>
            <div part="Y" xml:lang="lat">
                <head>MONUMENTA paroch. eccl. S. Petri.<index indexName="stw">
                        <term type="SWD" xml:lang="deu">Köln</term>
                        <index indexName="stw">
                            <term type="SWD" xml:lang="deu">Sankt Peter</term>
                        </index>
                    </index></head>
                <p> Inter huius ecclesiae imo urbis spectabiliora monumenta est majoris marmoreae
                    are <rs type="work" ref="#jaffe_1365">tabula, S. Petri vivam effigiem</rs><index
                        indexName="psw">
                        <term type="PND" xml:lang="deu">Rubens, Peter Paul</term>
                        <index indexName="stw">
                            <term type="SWD" xml:lang="deu">Kreuzigung Petri</term>
                        </index>
                    </index> exprimens donum <rs type="person" ref="#jabach_everhard">Everhardi
                        Jabachi</rs><index indexName="psw">
                        <term type="PND" xml:lang="deu">Jabach, Everhard (Bankier)</term>
                    </index> senatoris <rs type="place" ref="#koeln">Coloniensis</rs> divitis, et
                    artificiorum atque antiquitatum admiratoris et amatoris, ipsa vero pictura
                    tabulae, opus est clarissimi viri pictoris <rs type="person"
                        ref="#rubens_peter_paul">Petri Paulo Rubeni</rs><index indexName="psw">
                        <term type="PND" xml:lang="deu">Rubens, Peter Paul</term>
                    </index> Ubii, qui nostro aevo laudes et nomen Apellis<index indexName="psw">
                        <term type="PND" xml:lang="deu">Apelles</term>
                    </index> non immerito sibi artis praestantia acquisivit, et hunc uti Colonia
                    ferax est bonorum ingeniorum, in hac parochia, orbi dedit domus hereditaria
                    excellentissimi Domini <rs type="person" ref="#maximilianus_jodocus">Jodoci
                        Maximiliani</rs><index indexName="psw">
                        <term xml:lang="deu">Gronsfeld, Jodocus Maximilianus von</term>
                    </index> comitis in <rs type="place" ref="#gronsfeldt">Gronsfeldt</rs>, sita è
                    regione hospitii S. Ursulae, quam nuper Archiepiscopus Maguntinus inhabitavit
                    exul, et in qua serenissima <rs type="person" ref="#medici_maria">Maria
                        Medicaea</rs><index indexName="psw">
                        <term type="GND" xml:lang="deu">Medici, Maria /de'</term>
                    </index>
                    <rs type="place" ref="#frankreich">Galliarum</rs> Regina extremam vitae periodum
                    sanctissimè peregit et clausit. </p>
